0 "" {TEXT -1 271 "3.  Fundamental Theorem of Algebra.  The Fundamenta
l Theorem of Algebra asserts that every non-constant polynomial (with \+
complex-valued coefficients) has a root (a zero, a solution).  A conse
quence of the Fundamental Theorem of Algebra is that every polynomial \+
of degree " }{TEXT 276 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 13 " has exactly " }{TEXT 277 
1 "n" }{TEXT -1 108 " roots.  An alternate formulation of this consequ
ence would be that every non-constant polynomial of degree " }{TEXT 
279 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 38 " can be factored into a product of a  " }
{TEXT 278 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 16 " linear factors." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 35 "Consider the following po
lynomials:" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 6 "I.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "f := x^3-x^2-2*x" "6#>%\"fG,(*$%\"xG\"\"
$\"\"\"*$F'\"\"#!\"\"*&F+F)F'F)F," }{TEXT -1 4 "    " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "
" {TEXT -1 23 "     II.               " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 25 
"  III.                   " }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 0 
"" }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 7 "IV.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "F := x^4-14
4" "6#>%\"FG,&*$%\"xG\"\"%\"\"\"\"$W\"!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 12 "           \+
 " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 7 " V.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "G := 3*x^4+4
*x^3-2*x^2+x-6;" "6#>%\"GG,,*&\"\"$\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"%F(F(*&F+F(*$F*F'F
(F(*&\"\"#F(*$F*F/F(!\"\"F*F(\"\"'F1" }{TEXT -1 9 "         " }}{PARA 
0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 6 "VI.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "H := x^5-x^2-2*x" "6#>%
\"HG,(*$%\"xG\"\"&\"\"\"*$F'\"\"#!\"\"*&F+F)F'F)F," }{TEXT -1 24 "    \+
                    " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 257 "" 
0 "" {TEXT -1 172 "Factor each polynomial and determine whether Maple \+
was able to find enough linear factors to demonstrate the above assert
ion about the appropriate number of linear factors." }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 
"" 0 "" {TEXT -1 1 " " }}{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 18 "f := x^3-x^2-2*x ;" }}{PARA 
11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#>%\"fG,(*$)%\"xG\"\"$\"\"\"F**$)F(\"\"#F*!\"
\"*&F-F*F(F*F." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 18 "f := x^3-
x^2-2*x ;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#>%\"fG,(*$)%\"xG\"\"$\"\"
\"F**$)F(\"\"#F*!\"\"*&F-F*F(F*F." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" 
